For more information on this vehicle please contact 0877252552. Vehicle comes with a balance of a 3year Service and Warranty plan. The Mazda BT-50 is truly a double-cab that’s the complete package, bold, balanced, stylish and capable. Dare to be different than the norm. Stand out and turn heads with this workhorse, but with all the comfort of family bakkie. It comes with even more features like Apple Car Play, USB ports, Cruise Control, Key less access, keyless start/stop.
Apart from being much more handsomely styled than its predecessor, the new BT-50 offers appreciably more appeal for buyers who want the practicality and looks of a bakkie, but ultimately utilize their vehicles as family cars. A 4-door pick-up will never be able to match the sophistication of a unibody SUV, but Mazda’s newcomer demonstrates that “leisure double-cab” standards are rising rapidly.
